imdb.plot outline: More prime Minecraft videos for kids to enjoy. This fnaf roleplay hide and seek series features Five Nights at Freddy's mods and the little lizard club. Little Kelly, Little Turtle, Little Carly, Little Donny and more. Minecraft videos of Jen and Pat on the adventure.
